<h2> Petition to Commissioner Roger Goddell</h2>
<p>
  To: Roger Goodell<br/>
  Commissioner<br/>
  National Football League<br/>
  <br/>
  We the undersigned do hereby respectfully request that the NFL reconsider its Draft Day policies and agree to move the
  start time of the 1st Round of The NFL Draft from its current Thursday 7:00 p.m. slot back to Saturday at noon.<br/>
  <br/>
  Sincerely,<br/>
  The Undersigned
  <div style='text-align: center; margin-top: 10px;'>
    <%= link_to 'Sign the Petition', sign_petition_path() %> |
    <%= link_to 'View all Signatures', signatures_petition_path() %>
  </div>
</p>
<% if @post %>
<h2 class='left'><%= @post.title %></h2>
<p>
  <span class="dateline"><%= @post.created_at.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y  %I:%M%p") %></span>
  <br/><br/>
  <div class="intro"><%= @post.entry %></div>
  <br/>
  <p><%= @post.signature %></p>
  <br/>
  <%= link_to 'View', post_path(@post) %>
</p>
<% end %>